nsive is the new concentrated bleach more expensive cloroxs answer there will be the same number of uses per bottle in the concentrated bleach as there was before so the cost per use will be the same as our previous bleach products still seeking answers ask away how is clorox letting people know about the new concentrated formulation how is clorox letting people know about the new concentrated formulation cloroxs answer clorox will be letting consumers know about the change in a variety of ways on the bleach bottle it will say now concentrated and in many stores there will be additional signage in the laundry aisle in addition we will be letting consumers know via our tv advertising public relations materials website and facebook page still seeking answers ask away how is clorox® regularbleach different from clorox® scented bleach and clorox® splashless bleach how is clorox® regularbleach different from clorox® scented bleach and clorox® splashless bleach cloroxs answer our scented and splashless bleaches are not registered disinfectants if you need a registered disinfectant you can purchase clorox® regularbleach at almost any store that sells laundry products make sure that disinfects or kills germs appears on the label still seeking answers ask away ingredients  safety usage  packaging product benefits can i safely use clorox® regularbleach around children pets and pregnant women is it safe to mix clorox® regularbleach with other household cleaning products is clorox® regularbleach safe for septic systems can i use clorox® regularbleach to gargle brush my teeth or clean cuts and scrapes is clorox® regularbleach flammable what is the shelf life of clorox® regularbleach what organisms does clorox® regularbleach kill where can i find information and usage instructions for clorox® regularbleach concentrated where can i get coupons for clorox® regularbleach where can i buy clorox® regularbleach can clorox® regularbleach be used to disinfect water is the new concentrate